cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with the problem of guaranteeing safety in deep control policies, which is a core problem in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with deep machine learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also proposes a framework that utilizes control barrier functions, which is a common technique in control theory, suggesting that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with perception and control loops, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper implements the proposed method in a drone-racing environment, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
